{
  "stem": "27509.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But that doesn't mean, or it didn't mean to the people who came to buy, who were used that wherever they went-- or they went to buy shoes, they went to buy whatever it is, they had to bargain because it was part of the process.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They would have considered themselves foolish and-- and almost below-- below acceptance of their selves to be so-- so naive to accept the price without even trying to bargain.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that in itself was a-- an extraordinary sight to-- to watch and to listen and to see the-- the give and take of-- of-- of trying to-- to push the price down, and Father or whoever acted on his behalf, to hold on to his.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and it was quite-- quite a scene every time it occurred, and I never tired of it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Can you tell me about the suburb in which you lived?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the word 'suburb' in terms of the city of Bialystok, or for that matter any city of that-- because Bialystok was a city of 100,000 people, which in European terms, pre-war term-- terms, was a very, very substantial city.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because when I-- when I went, let's say, in 1959 to Geneva, Geneva didn't have many more people than Bialystok had, and Geneva was a world renowned center of-- of political importance and-- and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It had nicer-- nicer environment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It had a beautiful lake, which Bialystok didn't have.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But as far as number of people are concerned, 100,000 people was a very-- a very substantial-- substantial city.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But-- but there-- there were outlying parts of the city, obviously.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But as I've pointed out in the beginning, we lived right at the heart of the center of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was not suburb.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
